-----

**Table of Contents**

- [Installation](#installation)
- [License](#license)
- [Changelog](#changelog)

## Installation

```console
pip install edwh-bundler-plugin
```

But probably you want to install the whole edwh package:

```console
pipx install edwh[bundler]
# or
pipx install edwh[plugins,omgeving]
```

